        # first check if the optional is `Some` and then apply the function separately.
        # @type U: The type of the value contained in the optional returned by the predicate. This can be different from
        # the type of the value in this optional.
        # @type F: The type of the predicate function. This must be a function that takes a single argument of type `T`
